🛠️ What is n8n?
n8n (short for "node-node") is a powerful open-source workflow automation tool that allows you to connect various services and automate tasks with little to no code. It acts like a visual editor where you build workflows using a drag-and-drop interface.

🔑 Key Features
🔄 Low-code workflows: Build automations using nodes without writing code (but extendable with JavaScript functions when needed)

🌐 Integrations: Supports 350+ apps like Gmail, Google Sheets, Slack, Notion, Webhooks, and APIs

🔐 Self-hostable: Unlike Zapier or Make, you can deploy n8n on your own server for full control and privacy

📅 Triggers and actions: Use scheduled triggers, webhook events, or app-specific events to kick off workflows

🔁 Conditional logic: Handle complex decision-making with IF, Switch, and Merge nodes

⚙️ Use Cases
Automating email workflows

Scraping data from APIs and saving to databases

Syncing data between tools like Notion, Google Sheets, and Airtable

Lead generation, CRM automation, AI-powered pipelines
